Class Summary
FloodRiskAnalysisView Main class for starting a FloodRiskAnalysis with a user interface
GridCellRenderer ListCellRenderer for JComboBox with files as values(objects), displays only the filename of the file in JComboBox
GridFilter FileFilter, which accepts just AsciiGrid-Files (.asc)
GridRasterView JInternalFrame for displaying RectifiedGridCoverages
LogView View to inform the user about the actual process
MenuHandler MenuHandler for the FlooRiskAnalysisView
StatisticView View for displaying the statistic values like sum, minValue and maxValue for a choosen grid of the damageDirectory, the values are calculated for each landuseType and also for each administrationUnit, if an administrationUnitGrid is used
